    MadnessConstants, HTMLConstants

    public class MadnessWriterSkin1
extends MadnessWriter
    This HTML writer represents one means of "skinning" a Web site. Since it is the primary object for generating HTML output and is responsible for adding style sheet links, everything style-specific can be encapsulated in a CSS file and this class.
